%% Vibook — Sequence diagram: event booking and PayPal Sandbox payment
%% Mobile payment screen uses sandbox demo-approve for graduation demos.
%% Full create-order / capture-order flow is also supported by the backend.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Consumer
    participant Mobile as Mobile App
    participant Book as BookingController
    participant BookSvc as BookingService
    participant Pay as PayPalPaymentController
    participant PaySvc as PayPalPaymentService
    participant PayPal as PayPal Sandbox API
    participant DB as MySQL

    Note over Consumer,DB: Checkout — create PENDING booking

    Consumer->>Mobile: Tap Pay on payment screen
    Mobile->>Book: POST /api/v1/bookings<br/>{ eventId, timeSlotId, guestsCount }
    Book->>BookSvc: createBooking()
    BookSvc->>DB: validate event, slot, capacity
    BookSvc->>DB: insert bookings (status=PENDING)
    Book-->>Mobile: BookingResponse (id, PENDING)

    alt Graduation demo path (current mobile UI)
        Mobile->>Pay: POST /api/v1/payments/paypal/sandbox/demo-approve<br/>{ bookingId }
        Pay->>PaySvc: approveSandboxDemo()
        PaySvc->>DB: insert payments (CAPTURED, demo ids)
        PaySvc->>DB: update bookings status=CONFIRMED
        Pay-->>Mobile: PayPalCaptureOrderResponse
        Mobile->>Mobile: navigate to /confirmation
        Mobile-->>Consumer: booking confirmed
    else Full PayPal Sandbox path (supported by API)
        Mobile->>Pay: POST /api/v1/payments/paypal/create-order
        Pay->>PaySvc: createOrder()
        PaySvc->>PayPal: create order (HTTPS)
        PayPal-->>PaySvc: orderId + approvalUrl
        PaySvc->>DB: insert payments (status=CREATED)
        Pay-->>Mobile: approvalUrl
        Consumer->>PayPal: approve payment in browser
        Mobile->>Pay: POST /api/v1/payments/paypal/capture-order
        Pay->>PaySvc: captureOrder()
        PaySvc->>PayPal: capture order
        PayPal-->>PaySvc: COMPLETED
        PaySvc->>DB: update payments=CAPTURED
        PaySvc->>DB: update bookings status=CONFIRMED
        Pay-->>Mobile: PayPalCaptureOrderResponse
        Mobile-->>Consumer: booking confirmed
    end
